NOTE: This is only for= feedback, if you wish to launch a complaint please click here.
Chat for Queries/Complaints:
In order to expedite the process of communication and prompt assistance to = all of your online queries/complaints, NADRA Pak Identity has launched a qu= ick chat option, which is way quicker than the conventional approach of lau= nching a complaint via ticket system.
Please click =E2=80=9CChat here=E2=80= =9D, and you will be connected to one of our NADRA representat= ive for guidance and resolution of your query.

Now you can check status of your application from your application in= box. Please follow below link to login to PAK ID and check application stat= us. Or If you desire= to provide feedback/comments. Please click on the link given below and giv= e feedback.

Check Status Feedback

In order to streamline support requests and better serve you, NADRA&n= bsp;utilizes a support ticket system. Every support request is assigned a u= nique ticket number which you can use to track the progress and responses o= nline. For your reference we provide complete archives and history of all y= our support requests.A valid email address is required to submit a ticket.<= /p>

Launch Complaint

Before launching a complaint , please ensure that you have the follow= ing :

  • Your application Tracking id
  • Your Citizen Number
  • Your Contact number

Once a complaint is launched , you can track it=E2=80=99s status from NA= DRA website. To track your complaint, click here and then select =E2=80=9CCheck Ticket Status=E2= =80=9D
